snippet.title: Super Trench Attack! V2 Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Trench Attack! is a goofball twitch-shooter based on the folly of World War1, now available for Windows PC. Version 2.0 has new levels, gameplay and addtional content!

http://www.supertrenchattack.com/
